---
Source:
  Title: A Year with Rumi
  Translator: Coleman Barks
  Author: Rumi
  ISBN: 978-0060845971
  Publisher: HarperOne
  Page: 402
Format: Verse
By: Rumi
Title: Your True Life
Description: December 26
---
As you start to walk out on the way,
the way appears.

As you cease to be,
true life begins.

As you grow smaller,
this world cannot contain you.

You will be shown a being
that has no you in it.
